item.title: End UT-202 South at UT-201
item.description: End UT-202 South at UT-201 in Salt Lake County.

item.title: UT-202 South at I-80 East
item.description: UT-202 South at I-80 East to Salt Lake City. Continue south on UT-202 for Magna. UT-202 is spelled out on the sign as SR-202.

item.title: Begin UT-202 South at I-80
item.description: Begin UT-202 South at I-80 (Exit 104). Use I-80 west for Elko (Nevada); I-80 east for Salt Lake City. Elko is not typically used as a destination city on I-80 west of Salt Lake. Typically it is either Wendover, or Reno, Nevada.

item.title: I-80 West - Exit 104
item.description: I-80 West approaching Exit 104 - UT-202/To UT-201/Saltair Drive.

item.title: UT-201 West at UT-201 North
item.description: UT-201 West at UT-201 North in Salt Lake County.

item.title: UT-201 West Approaching UT-202
item.description: UT-201 West approaching UT-202. Use UT-202 north for I-80 East; use UT-201 west for I-80 West.

item.title: I-80 East - Exit 104
item.description: I-80 east at Exit 104 - UT-202/Saltair Drive.
